## Concatenation (abusing the Add trait)
impl Add for String
    def add(self: String, other: String) -> String
        return strCat(self, other)

impl Add for [T]
    def add(self: [T], other: [T]) -> [T]
        result := other

        for x in self.reverse()
            result = result.insert(x)

        return result


